<s docid="AP900805-0060" num="31" wdcount="15"> The law of the jungle takes over,'' she said, in remarks at the Aspen Institute.</s>
<s docid="AP900805-0060" num="32" wdcount="21"> The U.N. role in the Iraq-Kuwait crisis assumed increasing importance after divided Arab nations cancelled an emergency summit on the invasion.</s>
